review_text: It's a neat park for the whole neighborhood. It's ideal for families to go with their kids to the playfield and also for people who like to play football (soccer). Not very big.
Not enough tree on sunny day. Nice playground

(Translated by Google) The perfect place with young children! Very clean, well landscaped and fenced!

(Original)
L'endroit idéal avec de jeunes enfants! Très propre, bien aménagé et clôturé!

(Translated by Google) Beautiful large children's park surrounded by a fence that closes. Several modules for small and older, as well as water games. There is a nice grassy area with chairs and tall trees that offer shadows in summer.

(Original)
Beau grand parc pour enfants entouré d'une clôture qui se ferme. Plusieurs modules pour petits et plus vieux, ainsi que des jeux d'eau. Il y a un bel endroit gazonné avec des chaises et de grands arbres qui offrent des zones d'ombres en été.

(Translated by Google) Beautiful play structures and water games

(Original)
Belles structures de jeux et jeux d'eau
